Magistrate Jognilizwe Dumehleli has passed judgement in the bail application of Theo Jackson &amp; Willem Oosthuizen. The bail application of the two has been denied.Willem Oosthuizen and Theo Jackson appeared in the Middelburg Magistrates Court on Thursday, where Magistrate Dumehleli made his judgement. Magistrate Jogilizwe Dumehleli has said that the motive of the accused was very clear.The pair are accused of assaulting Rethabile Mlotshwa, before forcing him into a coffin and threatening to set him alight, which they filmed and posted on social media.Source: EyeWitness News